Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:30.85,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,Mom, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:33.98,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Nico!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.65,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,I'll turn back time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:37.15,RiskySubs,All,0,0,0,,What?!
