Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.90,RiskySubs,Nico's Father,0,0,0,,We can't assure you'll ever come back\Nto Universe Patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:44.81,RiskySubs,Kuromi,0,0,0,,Nico...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.27,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,It's fine, Kuromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:48.15,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,Because now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:50.15,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,when I see someone suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.90,RiskySubs,Nico,0,0,0,,I want to come to their rescue!
